WEBVTT

00:00.260 --> 00:03.961
You're a partner here.
The house needs to be maintained.

00:03.996 --> 00:06.564
It's a whorehouse,
not the Taj Mahal.

00:06.598 --> 00:08.867
Start showing me a return
on my investment.

00:08.902 --> 00:10.437
<i>That was beautiful.</i>

00:10.471 --> 00:12.606
I don't know who you are, mister,
but you just made a pal.

00:12.640 --> 00:15.676
I'm George Mueller with the
Farraday Electric Iron Company.

00:15.711 --> 00:17.113
Dean O'Banion.

00:17.147 --> 00:18.548
You fellas are going down

00:18.582 --> 00:19.849
and you're not
taking me with you.

00:19.883 --> 00:22.018
Starting soon I will be
accepting cash directly.

00:22.053 --> 00:23.220
<i>I have a middleman.</i>

00:23.254 --> 00:25.789
Dr. Mason,
I present to you

00:25.824 --> 00:29.061
<i>the future home of</i>
<i>St. Theresa's Women's Clinic.</i>

00:29.095 --> 00:31.697
Women's Health Clinic.
Free to all.

00:31.732 --> 00:33.099
Know what I'd like?

00:33.133 --> 00:35.869
To stay here forever.

00:35.903 --> 00:37.237
If I could.

00:38.473 --> 00:40.608
- This is a raid.

00:40.643 --> 00:43.745
Pay the fine direct to me
and we'll leave it at that.

00:43.779 --> 00:45.648
Why do I know you?

00:45.682 --> 00:48.751
- I have partners.

00:52.391 --> 00:54.859
I want what I paid for
and I want it now.

00:54.894 --> 00:58.897
- Nucky said to avoid Tabor Heights.
- You're not in charge.

00:58.932 --> 01:01.768
Gas up in Tabor Heights
and you stop for nobody.

01:01.802 --> 01:04.203
Wait!
It's an ambush!

01:04.238 --> 01:05.739
Stop!

01:07.676 --> 01:09.811
I have to talk to you.

