Johnny was bashful and shy ♪

18:52.829 --> 18:55.498
♪ Nobody understood why ♪

18:55.532 --> 18:58.501
♪ Mary loved him ♪

18:58.535 --> 19:02.605
♪ All the other girls
passed him by ♪

19:02.639 --> 19:06.609
♪ Everyone wanted
to know... ♪

19:06.643 --> 19:08.444
- Hold it!
- Can we stop?

19:08.479 --> 19:11.480
- Iron out the steps there, Vern.
- Yup.

19:11.515 --> 19:14.884
By the piano, please.
Move by the piano.

19:14.918 --> 19:16.886
It is not you.
It is not you.

19:16.920 --> 19:18.754
- Gonna go from right before
the dip. - Okay.

19:18.789 --> 19:21.290
You're leaning in here.
Going primp out,

19:21.324 --> 19:23.426
into the dip,
stay over the left leg.

19:23.460 --> 19:25.761
Look at me, darling.
Much better that way.

19:25.796 --> 19:27.563
<i>Here, let's go into</i>
<i>the next section.</i>

19:27.597 --> 19:30.165
<i>Please pay attention.</i>
<i>Left foot coming down the hill.</i>

19:30.200 --> 19:32.167
<i>It goes five, six, seven.</i>

19:32.201 --> 19:35.403
<i>♪ Not so good in a crowd,</i>
<i>but when you get him alone... ♪</i>

19:35.438 --> 19:36.872
<i>Round two, and...</i>

19:36.906 --> 19:39.674
- Pardon me.

19:39.708 --> 19:42.010
But would you mind waking me
up if something happens?

19:42.044 --> 19:45.246
Isn't it supposed
to be a comedy?

19:45.280 --> 19:47.748
♪ But then when
he takes you home ♪

19:47.782 --> 19:50.250
♪ You'd be surprised... ♪

19:50.285 --> 19:52.353
Well, I thought
I'd put something in.

19:52.387 --> 19:54.622
What are you going
to tell Shubert?

19:54.656 --> 19:56.590
That I've seen worse.

19:56.658 --> 19:58.659
Although that usually
involves a funeral.

19:58.693 --> 20:00.660
- What about Billie?
- <i>It's not her fault.</i>

20:00.695 --> 20:02.829
She puts it over in spades.

20:02.863 --> 20:05.832
But when they decided to call
it "The Naughty Virgin,"

20:05.866 --> 20:08.468
I don't think they had
the male lead in mind.

20:12.640 --> 20:14.941
What about the other one?

20:16.377 --> 20:19.546
<i>Vern?</i>
<i>I've worked with him.</i>

20:22.016 --> 20:23.550
Did he put his hands
on your waist?

20:23.584 --> 20:25.652
I'll never tell.

20:25.686 --> 20:27.854
<i>Very nice.</i>
<i>Please stay by the piano.</i>

20:27.888 --> 20:30.323
Do you think there's
something going on there?

20:30.357 --> 20:32.859
What do you mean?

20:32.893 --> 20:34.794
Look at her.

20:34.828 --> 20:36.796
That's a frisky little pony.

20:37.965 --> 20:39.799
<i>But the other one...</i>

20:39.833 --> 20:42.067
what do they call a horse
when they cut off his kishkes?

