<i>♪ Fools there were ♪</i>

58:24.248 --> 58:26.183
<i>♪ Fools there are ♪</i>

58:26.217 --> 58:29.686
<i>♪ Fools there'll</i>
<i>always be ♪</i>

58:29.720 --> 58:33.056
<i>♪ But the greatest</i>
<i>fool of all you see ♪</i>

58:33.091 --> 58:36.794
<i>♪ Has the flat across</i>
<i>the hall from me ♪</i>

